reviewText: Wow! 4 terrific Popeye favorites! Gotta love him! Watch him down that spinach and go into action! He's cool!
A Terrific super group of Popeye favorites! This VHS contains Taxi Turvy, Popeye for President, Assault and Flattery, and Out to Punch. 26min. Color. Produced in 1997 by CD Video Manufacturing
